headline: Nikki Glaser and David Spade Bringing New Las Vegas Residency to The Colosseum at Caesars Palace Beginning January 2026
summary: LAS VEGAS, September 22, 2025--Comedy favorites Nikki Glaser and David Spade are teaming up for a new residency at The Colosseum at Caesars Palace, returning to the Las Vegas Strip over three holiday weekends in 2026.
